  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/8b1a6d9bc2e8eeab466b5ff95910491e.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood, Fuel, Ammo & Speed is a fast-paced action roguelite FPS that is a love child between modern FPS franchises like Doom Eternal and roguelite games such as Vampire Survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Red Fuel has driven the world into a state of collapse and devastation; mankind has deformed into demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your weaponry and the art of combat are the only things that you can rely on.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.poster.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.webm?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.mp4?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bash through the hazards exploring the dynamic corners of the dystopian world. There is no time to waste, so don't wander off.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massacre the demons while wielding the most suitable weapon for the various encounters that emerge along the way.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to waste time on reloading and farming ammo. Hyper-focus on the battlefield, replenishing your ammo with the blood of your foes and the trustworthy Injector.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.poster.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.webm?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.mp4?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform stylish techniques, utilizing aggressive movement patterns - bullets are not your only asset.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demon Diamond and Demon Core - the concentrations of Red Fuel Energy, will empower you to ascend into a powerful being.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint the gruesome, gray world RED with demon blood!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/8b1a6d9bc2e8eeab466b5ff95910491e.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood, Fuel, Ammo & Speed is a fast-paced action roguelite FPS that is a love child between modern FPS franchises like Doom Eternal and roguelite games such as Vampire Survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Red Fuel has driven the world into a state of collapse and devastation; mankind has deformed into demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your weaponry and the art of combat are the only things that you can rely on.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.poster.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.webm?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/76989f5b8f1b52f04f5abc63962a2339.mp4?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bash through the hazards exploring the dynamic corners of the dystopian world. There is no time to waste, so don't wander off.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massacre the demons while wielding the most suitable weapon for the various encounters that emerge along the way.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to waste time on reloading and farming ammo. Hyper-focus on the battlefield, replenishing your ammo with the blood of your foes and the trustworthy Injector.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.poster.avif?t=1743255352\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.webm?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553840/extras/fb2d015020e430c3f79149e88d0f25a7.mp4?t=1743255352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform stylish techniques, utilizing aggressive movement patterns - bullets are not your only asset.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demon Diamond and Demon Core - the concentrations of Red Fuel Energy, will empower you to ascend into a powerful being.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint the gruesome, gray world RED with demon blood!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
